The paper discusses the issue of DDoS attacks in cloud computing environments, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of bandwidth and processing speed, which are related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The proposed method involves modifying an existing filtering method, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper aims to enhance the security of cloud computing, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
